Upon successful deployment:

The transaction is stored in tbl_ItemOut.

The stock quantity in tbl_ItemIn decreases.

A confirmation message is displayed: â€œItem successfully deployed.â€


The deployed itemâ€™s status becomes â€œOutâ€, and its Control No remains traceable via reports or search.



